{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"click事件","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Element/click_event","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>click</code></strong> 事件通常會在設備的按鈕（通常是滑鼠按鍵）點擊元素時執行。</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th>冒泡傳遞</th>\n      <td>是</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>可取消</th>\n      <td>是</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>介面</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>事件處理函式屬性</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Element/click_event\" title=\"onclick\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>onclick</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>如果按下了一個元素內的按鈕，且在釋放按鈕之前將指正移到元素之外，則會在在包含這兩個元素的最具體的父級元素上觸發事件。</p>\n<p><code>click</code>事件會在<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/mousedown_event\"><code>mousedown</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>和<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/mouseup_event\"><code>mouseup</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>事件之後觸發。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用說明","title":"使用說明","isH3":false,"content":"<p>傳遞給<code>click</code>事件處理函式的<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a>物件將其<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/detail\"><code>detail</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>屬性設置為點擊目標的次數。換句話說，<code>detail</code>在雙擊時為2，在三次點擊時為3，依此類推。該計數器在沒有任何點擊的情況下會在很短的時間間隔後重置；間隔時間的長短可能因瀏覽器和平台而異。間隔時間也很可能受到用戶偏好的影響；例如，無障礙選項可能會延長此間隔，以便更輕鬆地使用自適應介面執行多次點擊。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"internet_explorer","title":"Internet Explorer","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Internet Explorer 8 &amp; 9 suffer from a bug where elements with a computed <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a> of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">transparent (en-US)</a> that are overlaid on top of other element(s) won't receive <code>click</code> events. Any <code>click</code> events will be fired at the underlying element(s) instead. See <a href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/YUKma/show/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">this live example</a> for a demonstration.</p>\n<p>Known workarounds for this bug:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>For IE9 only:\n    <ul>\n      <li>Set <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a><code>: rgba(0,0,0,0)</code></li>\n      <li>Set <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/opacity\"><code>opacity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a><code>: 0</code> and an explicit <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a> other than <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">transparent (en-US)</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li>For IE8 and IE9: Set <code>filter: alpha(opacity=0);</code> and an explicit <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a> other than <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">transparent (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"safari_mobile","title":"Safari Mobile","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Safari Mobile 7.0+ (and likely earlier versions too) <a href=\"https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=153887\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">suffers from a bug</a> where <code>click</code> events aren't fired on elements that aren't typically interactive (e.g. <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a>) and which also don't have event listeners directly attached to the elements themselves (i.e. <a href=\"https://davidwalsh.name/event-delegate\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">event delegation</a> is being used). See <a href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/cvrhulu/k9t0sdnf/show/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">this live example</a> for a demonstration. See also <a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/AppleApplications/Reference/SafariWebContent/HandlingEvents/HandlingEvents.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40006511-SW6\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Safari's docs on making elements clickable</a> and the <a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/AppleApplications/Reference/SafariWebContent/HandlingEvents/HandlingEvents.html#/apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40006511-SW7\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">definition of \"clickable element\"</a>.</p>\n<p>Known workarounds for this bug:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Set <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/cursor\"><code>cursor</code></a><code>: pointer;</code> on the element or any of its ancestors.</li>\n  <li>Add a dummy <code>onclick=\"void(0)\"</code> attribute to the element or any of its ancestors up to but not including <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n  <li>Use a typically interactive element (e.g., <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>) instead of one that isn't typically interactive (e.g., <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a>).</li>\n  <li>Stop using <code>click</code> <a href=\"https://davidwalsh.name/event-delegate\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">event delegation</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Safari Mobile considers the following elements to be typically interactive (and thus they aren't affected by this bug):</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a> (but it must have an <code>href</code>)</li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/area\"><code>&lt;area&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (but it must have an <code>href</code>)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (but it must be associated with a form control)</li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><em>This list is incomplete; you can help MDN by doing further testing/research and expanding it.</em></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"範例","title":"範例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>此範例顯示對<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>的連續點擊次數。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Click<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> button <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'button'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nbutton<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  button<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Click count: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>detail<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"結果","title":"結果","isH3":true,"content":"<p>嘗試快速、重複地點擊按鈕以增加點擊次數。如果您在兩次點擊之間暫停一下，計數將重置。</p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"範例 sample\" id=\"frame_範例\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Element/click_event/_sample_.%E7%AF%84%E4%BE%8B.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/uievents/#event-type-click","title":"UI Events"}],"query":"api.Element.click_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器兼容性","id":"瀏覽器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Element.click_event","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Element/click_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/JavaScript/Building_blocks/Events\">事件介紹</a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/auxclick_event\"><code>auxclick</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/contextmenu_event\"><code>contextmenu</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/dblclick_event\"><code>dblclick</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/mousedown_event\"><code>mousedown</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/mouseup_event\"><code>mouseup</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/pointerdown_event\"><code>pointerdown</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/pointerup_event\"><code>pointerup</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用說明","id":"使用說明"},{"text":"範例","id":"範例"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器兼容性","id":"瀏覽器兼容性"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"click 事件通常會在設備的按鈕（通常是滑鼠按鍵）點擊元素時執行。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2